    <div style="display: none;">
        Verify Your Email Address
        
        Hi {{firstName}},
        
        Thanks for signing up for ModMaster Pro! Please verify your email address to activate your account.
        
        Click here to verify: {{verifyLink}}
        
        Or enter this code manually: {{verifyCode}}
        
        This code expires in {{expirationTime}}.
        
        Why verify your email?
        - Access all ModMaster Pro features
        - Receive important notifications
        - Enhanced account security
        - Start buying and selling parts
        
        Need help? Contact support@modmasterpro.com
        
